  <!-- EN: gravitational grenade belt -->
  <Milira_Apparel_AttractiveGrenade.label>引力手雷腰带</Milira_Apparel_AttractiveGrenade.label>
  <!-- EN: a series of grenades worn around the waist. When thrown, it can attract units within a certain range towards the center. -->
  <Milira_Apparel_AttractiveGrenade.description>一串挂在腰间的引力手雷。扔出后能够将一定范围内的单位向中心牵引。</Milira_Apparel_AttractiveGrenade.description>
