  <!-- EN: plasma shock grenade belt -->
  <Milira_Apparel_PlasmaShockGrenade.label>离子震爆手雷腰带</Milira_Apparel_PlasmaShockGrenade.label>
  <!-- EN: a series of grenades worn around the waist. When thrown, it explode and melt-down armor of targets. -->
